widgets_values: A snowboarder completes a difficult aerial spin in a half-pipe. The video is shot from a follow 视角，and the wide-angle lens creates a strong sense of immersion and visual impact. The snowboarder speeds up from the snow slope, performs a stretched-out flip and board grab in the blue sky with a graceful posture, and finally lands steadily in one go. The bright sunshine, the majestic snow-capped mountains in the background, together with the snowboarder's bright clothes and snowboard, form a magnificent picture combining strength and beauty, perfectly showing the speed, skills and free passion of snowboarding.

nodes.title: Note: About API Node
widgets_values:
[About API Node](https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/api-nodes/overview) 

To use the API, you must be in a secure network environment:

- Allows access from `127.0.0.1` or `localhost`.

- Use our API Node in website services starting with `https`

- Make sure you can normally connect to our API services (some regions may need a proxy).

- Make sure you are logged in in the settings and that your account still has enough credits to cover the consumption of API calls.

- On non-whitelisted sites or local area networks (LANs), please try to [log in using an API Key](https://docs.comfy.org/interface/user#logging-in-with-an-api-key).
